--- du -s prints bytes ---
1892	big.txt
--- du -sh is human-readable ---
1.8K	big.txt
--- ls -l prints bytes ---
- 1892 big.txt
--- ls -lh is human-readable ---
- 1.8K big.txt
--- cp -v names the copy ---
'big.txt' -> 'copy.txt'
--- mv -v names the move ---
renamed 'copy.txt' -> 'moved.txt'
--- utility error is located in the bash mood ---
shit: 1:1: error: cp: a source and a destination operand are required.
     1 |  shitbox cp
       |  ^~~~~~~~~~ here.
--- and a missing operand is located in the bash mood ---
shit: 1:1: error: ls: cannot access '/no/such/path': no such file or directory.
     1 |  shitbox ls /no/such/path
       |  ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ here.
